Abbott, in an appearance on Breitbart News Saturday on SiriusXM 125 the Patriot Channel, said that Texas is “the economic engine of America” and must reopen now that the coronavirus crisis is in decline.
Texas is the economic engine of America,” Abbott said.
“For America to get going, Texas has to get going.
“So what I rolled out yesterday is this massive team making sure Texas is going to take a lead as we open up the state, and Texas is doing business again,” Abbott said.
“We have a strike force that is focused on every business sector that exists in the state of Texas,” Abbott said.